features: New iPhone 15 Charger: 20W PD USB Type C power delivery wall plug with PD adapter 3.0 for quick charging. The USB-C port provides a maximum 20W output power, which is 3 times faster than a standard USB charger. It can charge your iPad Pro up to 50% in just 30 minutes. It operates at a maximum of 3A, helping you work efficiently.

Type C Fast Charging for iPad Series: uoyssimi use a C-port data cable with a faster charging rate, and it features a reversible C port at both ends (Either end can be connected to your product). Since the iPad 4th generation, iPad have been using the Type C interface. Therefore, this product can charge and transfer data for all your iPad higher than the 4th generation.

Optimal 10ft Length: In-depth market research reveals the unique advantages of a 10ft data cable, addressing specific user requirements. The extended reach of this cable enhances charging flexibility, proving ideal for scenarios where the power source is at a greater distance. Tailored for individuals needing an extended motion range without sacrificing charging capabilities, the 10ft length offers a balance between reach and efficiency. While not as compact as shorter alternatives, the 10ft option stands out for users prioritizing heightened mobility and versatility across diverse charging situations.

Wide Compatibility for Future-Proofing: This charger and cable are compatible with iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max, 2021/2020/2018 iPad Pro 12.9/11 inch, iPad Air 4, MacBook Air 13 inch, MacBook 12 inch, Gen 4/3, iPad Pro 11 Gen 2/1, Google Pixel 4/4 XL/3a XL/3/XL/2, Samsung Galaxy S8/S9/S10/S20 Plus, Note 10, LG, and other products that have a Type-C port. This wide compatibility ensures that your investment is future-proof, as it will work with a variety of devices you may own or upgrade to.
